{"tid":2237464,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超部份直播賽事10月起要收每人151港元 20隊只有李斯特城反對 曼聯先反對後接受","createTime":"2020-10-10T09:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T21:41:57.000Z","uid":223664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2e172e9269f85aa60b885af87c1466daf2c32816","tid":2237464,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"英超在英國本土的轉播從10月起，每輪將有5場比賽不會在電視直播。這些未在當地電視上直播的比賽，將以收費方式通過網絡提供給球迷，球迷要<span class=\"red\"><strong>花費14.95鎊（約151港元）</strong></span>才能觀看這些比賽。曼聯執行副主席活華特曾反對方案，後來說服不了其他球隊而轉為接受。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201010/DL5XBCFYQBD7NNKEUOALT25GOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201010%2FDL5XBCFYQBD7NNKEUOALT25GOE%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=5cd03e24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201010%2FDL5XBCFYQBD7NNKEUOALT25GOE%2F&h=7e710383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201010/DL5XBCFYQBD7NNKEUOALT25GOE/</a>"},{"pid":"bd092a12d5aac259e8813301bbe238eb08c28c5b","tid":2237464,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c254a16057c11f17d4836714e126d9189b85c0","tid":2237464,"uid":17142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線班英超隊"},{"pid":"193f8759a1eba1fa912e4210ae5f61957a04bda1","tid":2237464,"uid":4206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"後來說服不了其他球隊而轉為接受<br />\nIf you can&rsquo;t beat them, join them<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e9cc40ad0be8e4affabee051a4901a2bd55d8d","tid":2237464,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse